{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.1","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:1","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.006.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">R\u00e9ponse aux questions des Corinthiens sur le mariage<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-11: cf. Ge 2:18-25. Mt 19:3-12.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Pour ce qui concerne les choses dont vous m\u2019avez \u00e9crit, je pense qu\u2019il est bon pour l\u2019homme de ne point toucher de femme.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.2","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.6.20","name":"1 Corinthiens 6:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.6.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.2","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:2","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Toutefois, pour \u00e9viter l\u2019impudicit\u00e9, que chacun ait sa femme, et que chaque femme ait son mari.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.3","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.1","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.3","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:3","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Que le mari rende \u00e0 sa femme ce qu\u2019il lui doit, et que la femme agisse de m\u00eame envers son mari.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.4","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.2","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.4","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:4","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>La femme n\u2019a pas autorit\u00e9 sur son propre corps, mais c\u2019est le mari; et pareillement, le mari n\u2019a pas autorit\u00e9 sur son propre corps, mais c\u2019est la femme.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.5","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.3","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.5","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:5","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Ne vous privez point l\u2019un de l\u2019autre, si ce n\u2019est d\u2019un commun accord pour un temps, afin de vaquer \u00e0 la pri\u00e8re; puis retournez ensemble, de peur que Satan ne vous tente par votre incontinence.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.6","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.4","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.6","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:6","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Je dis cela par condescendance, je n\u2019en fais pas un ordre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.5","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.7","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:7","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Je voudrais que tous les hommes fussent comme moi; mais chacun tient de Dieu un don particulier, l\u2019un d\u2019une mani\u00e8re, l\u2019autre d\u2019une autre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.8","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.6","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.8","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:8","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>A ceux qui ne sont pas mari\u00e9s et aux veuves, je dis qu\u2019il leur est bon de rester comme moi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.9","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.9","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:9","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Mais s\u2019ils manquent de continence, qu\u2019ils se marient; car il vaut mieux se marier que de br\u00fbler.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.10","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.8","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.10","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:10","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>A ceux qui sont mari\u00e9s, j\u2019ordonne, non pas moi, mais le Seigneur, que la femme ne se s\u00e9pare point de son mari<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.11","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.9","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.11","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:11","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>(si elle est s\u00e9par\u00e9e, qu\u2019elle demeure sans se marier ou qu\u2019elle se r\u00e9concilie avec son mari), et que le mari ne r\u00e9pudie point sa femme.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.12","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.10","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.12","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:12","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.013,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 12-16: cf. 1 Pi 3:1, 2. (Ge 17:7. Ro 11:16.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Aux autres, ce n\u2019est pas le Seigneur, c\u2019est moi qui dis: Si un fr\u00e8re a une femme non-croyante, et qu\u2019elle consente \u00e0 habiter avec lui, qu\u2019il ne la r\u00e9pudie point;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.13","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.11","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.13","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:13","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>et si une femme a un mari non-croyant, et qu\u2019il consente \u00e0 habiter avec elle, qu\u2019elle ne r\u00e9pudie point son mari.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.12","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.14","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:14","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Car le mari non-croyant est sanctifi\u00e9 par la femme, et la femme non-croyante est sanctifi\u00e9e par le fr\u00e8re; autrement, vos enfants seraient impurs, tandis que maintenant ils sont saints.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.15","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.13","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.15","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:15","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Si le non-croyant se s\u00e9pare, qu\u2019il se s\u00e9pare; le fr\u00e8re ou la s\u0153ur ne sont pas li\u00e9s dans ces cas-l\u00e0. Dieu nous a appel\u00e9s \u00e0 vivre en paix.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.16","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.16","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:16","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Car que sais-tu, femme, si tu sauveras ton mari? Ou que sais-tu, mari, si tu sauveras ta femme?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.17","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.15","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.17","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:17","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.018,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 17-24: cf. Ph 4:11, 12. Ro 6:18, 22.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Seulement, que chacun marche selon la part que le Seigneur lui a faite, selon l\u2019appel qu\u2019il a re\u00e7u de Dieu. C\u2019est ainsi que je l\u2019ordonne dans toutes les \u00c9glises.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.18","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.16","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.18","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:18","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Quelqu\u2019un a-t-il \u00e9t\u00e9 appel\u00e9 \u00e9tant circoncis, qu\u2019il demeure circoncis; quelqu\u2019un a-t-il \u00e9t\u00e9 appel\u00e9 \u00e9tant incirconcis, qu\u2019il ne se fasse pas circoncire.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.19","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.17","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.19","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:19","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>La circoncision n\u2019est rien, et l\u2019incirconcision n\u2019est rien, mais l\u2019observation des commandements de Dieu est tout.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.20","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.18","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.20","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:20","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Que chacun demeure dans l\u2019\u00e9tat o\u00f9 il \u00e9tait lorsqu\u2019il a \u00e9t\u00e9 appel\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.21","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.19","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.21","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:21","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>As-tu \u00e9t\u00e9 appel\u00e9 \u00e9tant esclave, ne t\u2019en inqui\u00e8te pas; mais si tu peux devenir libre, profites-en plut\u00f4t.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.22","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.20","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.22","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:22","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Car l\u2019esclave qui a \u00e9t\u00e9 appel\u00e9 dans le Seigneur est un affranchi du Seigneur; de m\u00eame, l\u2019homme libre qui a \u00e9t\u00e9 appel\u00e9 est un esclave de Christ.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.23","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.21","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.23","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:23","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Vous avez \u00e9t\u00e9 rachet\u00e9s \u00e0 un grand prix; ne devenez pas esclaves des hommes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.24","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.22","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.24","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:24","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Que chacun, fr\u00e8res, demeure devant Dieu dans l\u2019\u00e9tat o\u00f9 il \u00e9tait lorsqu\u2019il a \u00e9t\u00e9 appel\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.25","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.23","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.25","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:25","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.026,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 25-40: cf. v. 1-11. (1 Pi 4:7. Lu 10:40-42.) H\u00e9 13:4.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Pour ce qui est des vierges, je n\u2019ai point d\u2019ordre du Seigneur; mais je donne un avis, comme ayant re\u00e7u du Seigneur mis\u00e9ricorde pour \u00eatre fid\u00e8le.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.26","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.24","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.26","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:26","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Voici donc ce que j\u2019estime bon, \u00e0 cause des temps difficiles qui s\u2019approchent: il est bon \u00e0 un homme d\u2019\u00eatre ainsi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.27","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.25","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.27","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:27","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Es-tu li\u00e9 \u00e0 une femme, ne cherche pas \u00e0 rompre ce lien; n\u2019es-tu pas li\u00e9 \u00e0 une femme, ne cherche pas une femme.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.28","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.26","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.28","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:28","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Si tu t\u2019es mari\u00e9, tu n\u2019as point p\u00e9ch\u00e9; et si la vierge s\u2019est mari\u00e9e, elle n\u2019a point p\u00e9ch\u00e9; mais ces personnes auront des tribulations dans la chair, et je voudrais vous les \u00e9pargner.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.29","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.27","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.29","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:29","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Voici ce que je dis, fr\u00e8res, c\u2019est que le temps est court; que d\u00e9sormais ceux qui ont des femmes soient comme n\u2019en ayant pas,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.30","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.28","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.30","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:30","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>ceux qui pleurent comme ne pleurant pas, ceux qui se r\u00e9jouissent comme ne se r\u00e9jouissant pas, ceux qui ach\u00e8tent comme ne poss\u00e9dant pas,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.31","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.29","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.31","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:31","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>et ceux qui usent du monde comme n\u2019en usant pas, car la figure de ce monde passe.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.32","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.30","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.32","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:32","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Or, je voudrais que vous fussiez sans inqui\u00e9tude. Celui qui n\u2019est pas mari\u00e9 s\u2019inqui\u00e8te des choses du Seigneur, des moyens de plaire au Seigneur;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.33","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.31","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.33","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:33","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>et celui qui est mari\u00e9 s\u2019inqui\u00e8te des choses du monde, des moyens de plaire \u00e0 sa femme.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.34","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.32","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.34","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:34","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>Il y a de m\u00eame une diff\u00e9rence entre la femme et la vierge: celle qui n\u2019est pas mari\u00e9e s\u2019inqui\u00e8te des choses du Seigneur, afin d\u2019\u00eatre sainte de corps et d\u2019esprit; et celle qui est mari\u00e9e s\u2019inqui\u00e8te des choses du monde, des moyens de plaire \u00e0 son mari.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.35","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:35","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.33","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.35","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:35","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>Je dis cela dans votre int\u00e9r\u00eat; ce n\u2019est pas pour vous prendre au pi\u00e8ge, c\u2019est pour vous porter \u00e0 ce qui est biens\u00e9ant et propre \u00e0 vous attacher au Seigneur sans distraction.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.36","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:36","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.34","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.36","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:36","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>Si quelqu\u2019un regarde comme d\u00e9shonorant pour sa fille de d\u00e9passer l\u2019\u00e2ge nubile, et comme n\u00e9cessaire de la marier, qu\u2019il fasse ce qu\u2019il veut, il ne p\u00e8che point; qu\u2019on se marie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.37","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:37","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.35","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:35","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.37","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:37","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.038,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>Mais celui qui a pris une ferme r\u00e9solution, sans contrainte et avec l\u2019exercice de sa propre volont\u00e9, et qui a d\u00e9cid\u00e9 en son c\u0153ur de garder sa fille vierge, celui-l\u00e0 fait bien.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.38","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:38","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.38"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.36","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:36","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"38","lastverse":"38","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.38","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.38","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:38","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.039,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.38\" class=\"v\">38<\/sup>Ainsi, celui qui marie sa fille fait bien, et celui qui ne la marie pas fait mieux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.39","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:39","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.39"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.37","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:37","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"39","lastverse":"39","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.39","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.39","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:39","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.038,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.007.040,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.39\" class=\"v\">39<\/sup>Une femme est li\u00e9e aussi longtemps que son mari est vivant; mais si le mari meurt, elle est libre de se marier \u00e0 qui elle veut; seulement, que ce soit dans le Seigneur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.40","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:40","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.40"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.38","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:38","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.38"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"40","lastverse":"40","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.40","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.40","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 7:40","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.039,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.008.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.7.40\" class=\"v\">40<\/sup>Elle est plus heureuse, n\u00e9anmoins, si elle demeure comme elle est, suivant mon avis. Et moi aussi, je crois avoir l\u2019Esprit de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8.1","name":"1 Corinthiens 8:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.39","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:39","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.39"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb9ccd686.23324156');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb9ccd686.23324156\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb9ccd686.23324156","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb9ccd686.23324156'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb9ccd686.23324156\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}